{
  "stem": "1895.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 354.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in fact, it was very dangerous for them to have liaison with Jews also.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I must add that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They kept this liaison for a while, even though-- even though they knew-- I suspect they knew what was in store for Jews.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They probably knew that from conversations with their-- with their German friends, the occupiers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they did kept- keep the liaison for some time, I guess because of-- of a friendship that my father had developed with them since they were children.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But eventually, they dropped it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was impossible to maintain it, because I remember we would go out in the middle of the night, outside the ghetto, and take off the armbands, which itself was a-- punished by death immediately.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we would go to the factory, which was outside of town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's in the middle of the night, and I remember in the wintertime.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was the winter of 1941.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we would go to the factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they would let us in, these Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They-- they would let us into the factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But they were so afraid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were so scared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They couldn't wait for the minute we left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They gave us the leather and then we left.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And-- and we knew that this wasn't going to continue, because if we got caught, they would torture us and make us say where we got the leather, so they would get implicated also.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So the whole thing was just terrible, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And after a while, it-- we couldn't do it anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I understand.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The restrictions-- the restrictions were evident more and more.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
